---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section>
    <div class="about-container">
      <img
        src="public/pictures/IMG_20230921_155205 (1).jpg"
        alt="Onur Kantarci"
        class="profile-pic"
      />
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p>
        Hello! I'm Onur Kantarci, a passionate and dedicated full-stack
        developer from Prizren, Kosovo. With a background in law and a
        self-taught journey into the world of web development, I have developed
        a diverse skill set that allows me to tackle complex projects with
        creativity and precision.
      </p>
      <p>
        My journey in tech began with a deep curiosity and drive to create
        impactful digital solutions. Over the past few years, I have honed my
        skills in various technologies, including Vue, React, HTML, CSS,
        JavaScript, TypeScript, and Python. My expertise extends to building
        robust backend systems with Express.js, managing databases with MongoDB
        and PostgreSQL, and containerizing applications with Docker for seamless
        deployment.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've had the privilege of learning from a senior full-stack developer
        and being mentored by my brother, which has significantly shaped my
        approach to development. I enjoy taking on freelance projects where I
        can apply my knowledge and continue to grow.
      </p>
      <p>
        Some of my notable projects include a comprehensive Vue-Express Docker
        setup, a Python-based task scheduling system, a secure Express.js
        application with DDoS protection, and a variety of web applications
        featuring authentication, data management, and real-time communication.
      </p>
      <div class="skills">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Vue.js</li>
          <li>React</li>
          <li>HTML & CSS</li>
          <li>JavaScript & TypeScript</li>
          <li>Python</li>
          <li>Express.js</li>
          <li>MongoDB & PostgreSQL</li>
          <li>Docker</li>
          <li>REST API</li>
          <li>JSON WEB TOKEN</li>
          <li>WebSocket</li>
          <li>Bootstrap</li>
          <li>RabbitMQ</li>
          <li>IndexedDB</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    animation: fadeIn 500ms ease-in-out;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 60%;
    font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 8px 10px rgba(50, 84, 135, 0.1);
  }

  .profile-pic {
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  h1,
  h2 {
    color: #333;
  }

  p,
  li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .skills {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .skills ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .skills li {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 10px;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .social-links img {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
  }

  .contact {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      max-width: 90%;
    }
  }
</style>
